00:36:25.890 --> 00:36:27.530 align:middle line:84%
We know that if
a set is uniform,

00:36:27.530 --> 00:36:31.650 align:middle line:84%
and the rho covering
number grows for every rho,

00:36:31.650 --> 00:36:33.970 align:middle line:84%
and in fact, we
