00:37:48.186 --> 00:37:54.740 align:middle line:84%
And OK, by using this
idea for every rho,

00:37:54.740 --> 00:37:57.350 align:middle line:84%
so we did it for delta,
but the assumption

00:37:57.350 --> 00:37:59.230 align:middle line:84%
is called for
every rho, at least

00:37:59.230 --> 00:38:01.310 align:middle line:84%
for every rho which is
