00:41:01.660 --> 00:41:06.500 align:middle line:84%
And then we know that A plus
little aA grows at every scale.

00:41:06.500 --> 00:41:11.060 align:middle line:84%
If it was true that a plus
little aA was uniform,

00:41:11.060 --> 00:41:13.280 align:middle line:84%
then we would win,
